name: Girl Birth Announcement (customised)
description:
This birth announcement is fully customisable, just follow the simple instructions below. Please let me know if you have any questions prior to purchasing. 

1.	Purchase this item in your choice of size (4” x 6” or A6)
2.	Email your favourite, high resolution (under 10mb) photo of your baby to hello@littlepaperproject.com.au In the email also include the following details:
-	Your baby’s name
-	Birth date
-	Time of birth
-	Weight of baby
-	Length of baby
-	Short message (see example)
-	Colour choice (blue, green or orange)
Please let me know if you would like your photo to be colour corrected or converted to black and white.

You will receive a proof within 2 working days. One round of minor text changes is included in the price.

The approved version will be supplied at both high resolution and web quality (suitable for emailing).

name: Birthday invite postcard (customised)
description:
This A6 (148 x 105mm) birthday/special event postcard is fully customisable, just follow the simple instructions below. Please let me know if you have any questions prior to purchasing. 

1.	Purchase this item
2.	Email the following details to hello@littlepaperproject.com.au
-	Event title for the centre of the card (approx 3 – 5 words)
-	Date (in the format you would like it to be written)
-	Address
-	RSVP details
-	Text for speech bubble (bottom left)
-	Text to accompany images on the right hand side 
-	Any special requests (background or ribbon colour change, minor layout changes)

You will receive a proof within 2 working days. One round of minor text changes is included in the price.

The approved version will be supplied at both high resolution and web quality (suitable for emailing).
